      • DB

        public DB(Store store,
          boolean storeOpened,
          boolean isThreadSafe,
          java.lang.ClassLoader classLoader,
          int shutdownHook)

        A database with easy access to named maps and other collections.

        Parameters:
        store - Stores all underlying data
        storeOpened - True if store existed before and was opened,false if store was created and is completely empty
        isThreadSafe - returns true if this is configured to be thread safe
        shutdownHook - type of shutdown hook,0 is disabled,1 is hard ref,2 is weak ref
